This archive contains all files of the git-lock client.
These files have to be distributed to all git clients which like to participate.

bin: 
	All files in bin need to be on the PATH on each client.
	> $ export PATH=$PATH:/opt/git-lock-client/bin
	
	Additionally, the environment variable LOCK_CLIENT_BIN_DIR need to be set to the bin directory.
	> $ export LOCK_CLIENT_BIN_DIR=/opt/git-lock-client/bin
